F_{n-1} +2F_{n-2} + ... + (n-1+1)\cdot F_{0} = 3^{n-1}
 F_{n-1} +2F_{n-2} + ... + n\cdot F_{0} = 3^{n-1} 
F_{n} +2F_{n-1} + ... + (n+1)\cdot F_{0} -(F_{n-1} +2F_{n-2} + ... + n\cdot F_{0} ) =3^{n} - 3^{n-1} 
F_n+F_{n-1}+F_{n-2}+\ldots+F_0=2\cdot 3^{n-1}\;.
